title: Experience the updated Kefalonia Airport (LGKF) by flying in with MSFS.
description:
This video will explore Kefalonia Airport (LGKF) in Greece, which has recently been updated in MSFS. To my knowledge, it is among the first airports to receive such an update in the simulator.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
